rComments: I'll follow him wherever he goes :p I'm not in love with him, don't worry. He's so nice and so easy. Students in the class are so rude to him because he's too nice. His exams are easy as long as you know the material. His notes aren't dependable.... I usually rely on the book. Just study (from the book) and you'll do well.

Hard class, esp. the assignments, but nice prof. Notes posted on time, but very brief explanations. If you miss the lecture you 'll need to read the material on your own. Was always available to help during office hours with the assignment and concept in the course. I liked practical applications in Excel, useful.
Very young, good looking prof ;) but HORRIBLE prof.can't communicate concepts/goals at all. He's smart but can't teach for****! Also, talks down to students, expects you to be at his level.
